asella","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":0.6768,"vote_count":144,"poster_path":"/hYNJ4KNMVaVgR5JAqC5qlgbJEmJ.jpg","release_date":"1993-11-24","vote_average":4.313,"backdrop_path":"/wyF3MzxcLZyJnEYZsp6XdPvpsdc.jpg","original_title":"Cyborg 2","original_language":"en"},{"id":1489530,"adult":false,"title":"The War of the Boundary","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[28],"popularity":0.2986,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/g51wizld90EFp2Lth0Fk5PwiifC.jpg","release_date":"1978-07-22","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"戰天山","original_language":"zh"},{"id":266225,"adult":false,"title":"Death of Yazdgerd","video":false,"overview":"Bahram Beyzai's poetic imagining of the circumstances that led to the death of Yazdgerd III, the last of the Sassanid kings of Iran. His death in 651, during the Arab invasions that brought Islam to this Zoroastrian realm, was mysterious: his corpse was discovered in a mill, but the cause of his death—and the whereabouts of his remains—are unknown.","genre_ids":[36,18],"popularity":0.2616,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/7CX0iN3bq9Twg2a1kusTe82dEI4.jpg","release_date":"1982-04-01","vote_average":7.8,"backdrop_path":"/8zteMEIB7WYGDQnEGi5vN0HEict.jpg","original_title":"مرگ یزدگرد","original_language":"fa"},{"id":18248,"adult":false,"title":"The Foreigner","video":false,"overview":"This story is about a freelance agent who is the courier of a package from France to Germany. He soon finds that many people want to get their hands on it.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":1.2201,"vote_count":163,"poster_path":"/esfi6vzwvq5M6H5OisFvG58mSvt.jpg","release_date":"2003-06-01","vote_average":3.96,"backdrop_path":"/5ghwjT9Sw4OqXkhqKrkQEJb8CBL.jpg","original_title":"The Foreigner","original_language":"en"},{"id":266396,"adult":false,"title":"The Gunman","video":false,"overview":"Eight years after fleeing the Congo following his assassination of that country's minister of mining, former assassin Jim Terrier is back, suffering from PTSD and digging wells to atone for his violent past. After an attempt is made on his life, Terrier flies to London to find out who wants him dead -- and why. Terrier's search leads him to a reunion with Annie, a woman he once loved, who is now married to an oily businessman with dealings in Africa.","genre_ids":[28,18,80],"popularity":2.1268,"vote_count":1007,"poster_path":"/fhwRY5aprUyUG7maRWCmtoTb4lh.jpg","release_date":"2015-02-16","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/2g1ZVQV1svzOfyd9WL5dAV1OkL1.jpg","original_title":"The Gunman","original_language":"en"},{"id":19403,"adult":false,"title":"The Mechanic","video":false,"overview":"Arthur Bishop is a veteran hit man who, owing to his penchant for making his targets' deaths seem like accidents, thinks himself an artist. It's made him very rich, but as he hits middle age, he's so depressed and lonely that he takes on one of his victim's sons, Steve McKenna, as his apprentice. Arthur puts him through a rigorous training period and brings him on several hits. As Steven improves, Arthur worries that he'll discover who killed his father.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":1.5477,"vote_count":326,"poster_path":"/hizE0MwFJOBlfLSFqFNKv7cSxkT.jpg","release_date":"1972-10-06","vote_average":6.7,"backdrop_path":"/thMdGESFFPyMTt14AACD0qk9v0m.jpg","original_title":"The Mechanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":437109,"adult":false,"title":"The Villainess","video":false,"overview":"Honed from childhood into a merciless killing machine by a criminal organization, assassin Sook-hee is recruited with the promise of freedom after ten years of service. However, secrets from her past destroy everything she’s worked for and now she embarks on a roaring rampage of revenge.","genre_ids":[28,80,18,53],"popularity":1.9992,"vote_count":747,"poster_path":"/tJlOV2SU6qTxR540H9VtoCAOVm.jpg","release_date":"2017-06-08","vote_average":6.915,"backdrop_path":"/labMpUVoAqNlHTKiu7KsoZT0v9d.jpg","original_title":"악녀","original_language":"ko"},{"id":19550,"ad