9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"The Assassin | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"9th century China. Ten year old general’s daughter Nie Yinniang is abducted by a nun who initiates her into the martial arts, transforming her into an exceptional assassin charged with eliminating cruel and corrupt local governors. One day, having failed in a task, she is sent back by her mistress to the land of her birth, with orders to kill the man to whom she was promised – a cousin who now leads the largest military region in North China. After 13 years of exile, the young woman must confront her parents, her memories and her long-repressed feelings."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/105866/the-assassin"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"The Assassin"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"9th century China. Ten year old general’s daughter Nie Yinniang is abducted by a nun who initiates her into the martial arts, transforming her into an exceptional assassin charged with eliminating cruel and corrupt local governors. One day, having failed in a task, she is sent back by her mistress to the land of her birth, with orders to kill the man to whom she was promised – a cousin who now leads the largest military region in North China. After 13 years of exile, the young woman must confront her parents, her memories and her long-repressed feelings."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/105866/the-assassin"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/10RcGMfzg2lIW1aLcR4ILfNbHK2.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","conten